trans-unit.source: Export Information of Users, Agents, and Agent Groups

seg-source.mrk: Export Information of Users, Agents, and Agent Groups

target.mrk: Exporter des iinformations sur les utilisateurs, les agents et les groupes d'agents

trans-unit.source: In the <MadCap:variable name="General.ProductName" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> <MadCap:variable name="ALN.adm_exe" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" />, you can easily export information of agents, groups, user profiles, users, tenants, replication destinations, restore tokens or protections (<MadCap:xref href="#Export_information" class="figure_x" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">see Figure</MadCap:xref>).

seg-source.mrk: In the <MadCap:variable name="General.ProductName" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> <MadCap:variable name="ALN.adm_exe" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" />, you can easily export information of agents, groups, user profiles, users, tenants, replication destinations, restore tokens or protections (<MadCap:xref href="#Export_information" class="figure_x" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">see Figure</MadCap:xref>).

target.mrk: Dans la <MadCap:variable name="ALN.adm_exe" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> <MadCap:variable name="General.ProductName" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" />, vous pouvez facilement exporter des informations sur les agents, les groupes, les profils d'utilisateurs, les utilisateurs, les entités, les destinations de réplication, les jetons de restauration ou les protections (<MadCap:xref href="#Export_information" class="figure_x" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">see Figure</MadCap:xref>).

trans-unit.source: Information can be exported to HTML and CSV formats

seg-source.mrk: Information can be exported to HTML and CSV formats

target.mrk: Les informations peuvent être exportées aux formats HTML et CSV.

trans-unit.source: If no specific content has been selected, the entire list is exported by default.

seg-source.mrk: If no specific content has been selected, the entire list is exported by default.

target.mrk: Si aucun contenu spécifique n'a été sélectionné, la liste entière est exportée par défaut.
